wherein said electrophotographic photosensitive drum is contacted along a length thereof to said transferring means for receiving a bias voltage to transfer a developed image provided by said developing means onto a recording material; 
wherein said storing means is disposed closer to said electrophotographic photosensitive drum than a tangent line passing through a contact point between said electrophotographic photosensitive drum and said transferring means and extending in a direction crossing with the longitudinal direction of said electrophotographic photosensitive drum; and 

(d) feeding means for feeding the recording material.

